{"id":310228,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-薄案开庭，法庭外访民喊冤，多人被警方/","date":"2013-08-23T14:48:59Z","modified":"2013-08-24T21:11:59Z","title":"维权网 | 薄案开庭，法庭外访民喊冤，多人被警方扣押（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙雨报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日薄熙来在济南市中级法院被受审。济南及各地民众前往围观，一大早通往山东省济南市中级法院的各个路口全被戒严。各界人士在警戒线以外，遍地的警察在维稳。附近的酒店里警察整齐的坐在马扎上待命。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>无法参加旁听和到法院门前的各地上访维权人士，纷纷在警戒线外喊冤。约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，一对儿父女打出状纸，被便衣迅速带走。外媒记者追赶着拍照，由此拉开了维权访民喊冤的序幕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民们围着一外国记者诉冤，一女访民举着“拆迁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>年至今没安置”的状纸。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>山东青岛的林秀丽举出“山东青岛司法腐败，杀人凶手逍遥法外，被害人被政府非法关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">932</span><span>天”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>天津张文艳为被天津武警医院治疗死亡的父亲喊冤“一条人命死在武警医院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>年无人管”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>另一妇女在喊冤时被便衣拖走，一路上中外记者追赶着拍照解围，但没有奏效，人被拖倒在地抓到车上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>此时喊冤声浪进入高潮。一男访民上到近三米高的墙上，手举材料呐喊，几百警察赶到现场，济南市委书记前来做工作，那访民要解决问题方案，否则就是不下来。消防警开车赶来，架上云梯强行将人带下来，押到车上带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点，在济南火车站旁边的马路上，陕西康素萍被巡逻警察送到济南市市中区公安分局经二路派出所关押。上午，康素萍在电话中说，警察正把她带上警车，不知要带往何处。突然康素萍失声哭起来，她说害怕被移交给陕西地方，在两年的上访过程中，曾被陕西地方殴打关押，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>次关进黑监狱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>次行政拘留，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次差一点被送进精神病院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据康素萍说，和她一起关在经二路派出所的另外还关押了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人，一对浙江籍的母女，辽宁籍一名男子、河南籍一名男子，他们都是因为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日白天到法庭现场的，夜晚分别在宾馆被抓的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在法院外喊冤的一些人表示，人们围观薄案审理，就是想见证司法的公平公正。薄熙来案能否推动中国法治进程，众人表示怀疑。但能推动个案进展也是好事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EyDSpyutSJ4/Uhdx8c3RGtI/AAAAAAAAnOE/YyD7nS4bwtg/s1600/IMG0.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EyDSpyutSJ4/Uhdx8c3RGtI/AAAAAAAAnOE/YyD7nS4bwtg/s320/IMG0.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hsC5tqS9hrQ/Uhdx9sWceLI/AAAAAAAAnOU/2wSk5Uc86F4/s1600/IMG00073.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hsC5tqS9hrQ/Uhdx9sWceLI/AAAAAAAAnOU/2wSk5Uc86F4/s320/IMG00073.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-64IjM_5fmQw/Uhdx-uIaa8I/AAAAAAAAnOc/jDiEiOHDo6g/s1600/IMG00076.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-64IjM_5fmQw/Uhdx-uIaa8I/AAAAAAAAnOc/jDiEiOHDo6g/s320/IMG00076.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tjki70zj3_Q/Uhdx-4D10oI/AAAAAAAAnOg/u1aiq49fUvA/s1600/IMG00081.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tjki70zj3_Q/Uhdx-4D10oI/AAAAAAAAnOg/u1aiq49fUvA/s320/IMG00081.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hGMOVY0SMe8/Uhdx84i8cjI/AAAAAAAAnOM/1YGHROorIWk/s1600/IMG00064.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hGMOVY0SMe8/Uhdx84i8cjI/AAAAAAAAnOM/1YGHROorIWk/s320/IMG00064.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.l